---
import FullScreenLayout from "@layouts/FullScreenLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<FullScreenLayout title="Color Validator">
  <div class="page-layout">
    <div class="headings">
      <h1>Board Game Data Tools</h1>
      <h2>Data analytics for recorded plays at BoardGameGeek</h2>
      <div class="flex align-center gap-4 text-2xl">
        <a
          class="text-2xl"
          href="https://www.bgdatatools.com/acciopatronus"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"><Icon name="tabler:meeple" /></a
        >
        <a
          class="text-2xl"
          href="https://github.com/zapbampow/bg-data-tools"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          ><Icon name="tabler:brand-github-filled" /></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>
      Since 2009 I've used BoardGameGeek to record every game I've
      played...okay, almost every game. At first it was only that I had played a
      game. Then it included who I played with. Then I added where we were and
      who won.It has turned into quite a bit of data on my game plays (over 3000
      games played since 2009).
    </p>

    <p>
      One day one of my kids said, "Dad always wins." It got me wondering, "How
      frequently does each of us win?" There was no easy way for me to answer
      that question. However, BGG has a free API. So I set out to build an app
      to answer that question and other weird questions I might have.
    </p>

    <p>
      When playing cooperative games with my family, how often do we win or
      lose? What games have I played with Mike? Have I introduced Tami to Sky
      Team yet? What did I play last weekend again?
    </p>

    <p>
      Over time I built it be my go to tool for all questions about my gaming
      history.
    </p>
  </div>
</FullScreenLayout>

<style>
  .headings {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }
  }

  .page-layout {
    margin-block: 10rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;

    pre {
      padding-inline: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* breakout grid */
  .page-layout > *,
  .full-width > * {
    grid-column: content;
  }
  .page-layout,
  .full-width {
    --minimum-content-padding: 1rem;

    /** TRACK WIDTHS **/
    --full-max-width: 1fr;
    --popout-max-width: 900px;
    --content-max-width: 650px;
    --inset-content-max-width: 500px;

    /** TRACK SIZES **/
    --full: minmax(var(--minimum-content-padding), 1fr);
    --popout: minmax(
      0,
      calc((var(--popout-max-width) - var(--content-max-width)) * 0.5)
    );
    --content: minmax(
      0,
      calc((var(--content-max-width) - var(--inset-content-max-width)) * 0.5)
    );
    --inset-content: min(
      var(--inset-content-max-width),
      100% - var(--minimum-content-padding) * 2
    );

    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns:
      [full-start]
      var(--full)
      [popout-start]
      var(--popout)
      [content-start]
      var(--content)
      [inset-content-start]
      var(--inset-content)
      [inset-content-end]
      var(--content)
      [content-end]
      var(--popout)
      [popout-end]
      var(--full)
      [full-end];
  }

  /** CLASSES **/
  .page-layout .full {
    grid-column: full;
  }
  .page-layout .full-start {
    grid-column-start: full-start;
  }
  .page-layout .full-end {
    grid-column-end: full-end;
  }

  .page-layout .popout {
    grid-column: popout;
  }
  .page-layout .popout-start {
    grid-column-start: popout-start;
  }
  .page-layout .popout-end {
    grid-column-end: popout-end;
  }

  .page-layout .content {
    grid-column: content;
  }
  .page-layout .content-start {
    grid-column-start: content-start;
  }
  .page-layout .content-end {
    grid-column-end: content-end;
  }

  .page-layout .inset-content {
    grid-column: inset-content;
  }
  .page-layout .inset-content-start {
    grid-column-start: inset-content-start;
  }
  .page-layout .inset-content-end {
    grid-column-end: inset-content-end;
  }

  .page-layout .full-width {
    grid-column: full;
  }
  .page-layout .full-content,
  .full-content-nopad {
    grid-column: full;
  }
  .page-layout .full-content {
    padding-inline: var(--minimum-content-padding);
  }
</style>
